INSTALLATION of Battles of Antargis
===================================

On Ubuntu ( Debian ? )
----------------------

First install some dependencies:

> sudo apt-get install g++ libsdl1.2-dev libsdl-image1.2-dev libsdl-mixer1.2-dev libsdl-ttf2.0-dev libpng12-dev cmake libboost.*signal.*dev fluid-soundfont-gm musescore-soundfont-gm

continue with 'Linux'

Linux
-----

Then compile the game using debug-symbols - as it is in active development

> ./makeDebug.sh

Then run the game:

> ./Debug/antargis
